# Black Gold Connect

Official Black Gold Connect website, digital business cards, and team directory.

## Brand colours

- Black Gold Gold: `#C69653` / RGB `198, 150, 83`
- Response Green: `#6EBE44` / RGB `110, 190, 68`
- Black: `#000000`

## Publishing

This site is published with GitHub Pages from the `main` branch and the repository root.

## Updating a team member

Each team member has a folder under `/people/`. Update the relevant `index.html` page and matching vCard under `/vcards/`.

## NFC card links

Use the employee profile URL on the NFC card. Example:

`https://bggoplan.github.io/black-gold-connections/people/jason/`
